"With which impregnate, from their groins they shed A slimy juice, by faise conception bred. The shepherd knows it well, and calis by name Hippomanes, to note the mother's flame. \"This, gather'd in the planetary hour, Withnoxious weeds,and speli'd with words of power, Dire stepdames in the magic bowl infuse, And mix, for deadly dranghts, the poisonous juice."